Pathway explored : REACTOME REGULATION OF TP53 ACTIVITY THROUGH PHOSPHORYLATION

This pathway contain 91 genes.

In these 91 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes DE significant with a major participation in the enrichment (leadingEdge cal by fgsea filter by padj<0.05).
